{
  "stem": "12447.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I even went out with my sister quite a few times in the beginning, playing the same game.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was also-- she was kind of dirty blond--looking, and she spoke as good Polish as I did.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we had no problem going out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Coming back, we had no problem getting in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's, like-- played it for quite a few weeks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then things were already getting tougher and tougher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wouldn't let us out anymore because I suppose these people working in the ghetto had to evacuate or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I remember I came over once to a Polish policeman and tried to get out, and I got a good snap in my face for lying.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he didn't care if I was Jewish or Polish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As long as I was on the ghetto side, he assumed that I was a Jew and I was lying to him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I did not take any more chances doing that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I tried all kinds of tricks that I could to get out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Many times I'd get out walking alongside the wall and trying to sneak behind the backs of everybody.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that took quite a bit of sneaking through.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So many times I would approach the gate getting by the Polish-- the Jewish policeman, getting by the Polish policemen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was a situation that they were bringing in into the ghetto carts of food, carts of different transportation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were in and out, coming out with documents, and going in with documents.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they got busy-- I had to wait for a situation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they got a little bit busy, a little commotion, I'd run through.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So many times, I went through with my sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
